original_title: セカイシンフォニー Sekai Symphony 2021 Live
overview: Sound source & visualization of Sekai Symphony!  The orchestra concert "Sekai Symphony" will be held on Saturday, October 16th at Pacifico Yokohama National Convention Hall with two performances, day and night. This performance will be released in two forms, CD and Blu-ray!
title: Sekai Symphony 2021 Live
